Leslie Lyles https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leslie_Lyles 0 Leslie Lyles is an American film actress. She appeared in more than forty films and television serials between 1987 and 2011. She is the ex-wife of actor Keith Reddin. Leslie_Lyles is an_American_film_actress . She appeared in more_than_forty_films_and_television_serials between 1987_and_2011 .
